# Docker build context for Railway flex wrapper only.
# Every script the Dockerfile.railway COPY references MUST be un-ignored here,
# or a cache-missing (fresh) build fails at COPY with "file not found in build
# context" and Railway silently falls back to the last image. Keep this list in
# sync with the COPY line in Dockerfile.railway.
*

!Dockerfile.railway
!railway-entrypoint.sh
!railway-flex-bootstrap.sh
!railway-preinstall-db.sh
!railway-ensure-ssl.sh
!railway-configure-apache.sh
!railway-install-copilot.sh
!patch-flex-openemr.sh
